# Python desktop — cấu trúc

```
imeiTool/
  main.py              # freeze_support, crash log, prime_macos_app_name
  imei_tool.spec       # PyInstaller (+ PYARMOR_OBF_DIR)
  build_mac.sh         # pyarmor → pyinstaller → PDF hướng dẫn
  docs/api.md          # contract API
  assets/              # AppIcon, logo
  scripts/             # pyarmor, generate_user_guide_pdf, icon
  src/
    gui.py             # ImeiToolWindow, run_app()
    app_branding.py    # APP_NAME, VERSION, BUNDLE_ID
    bundle_paths.py    # is_frozen(), MEIPASS
    theme.py           # QSS dark theme
    database.py        # SQLite + app_orders
    order_sync.py      # engine đơn IMEI
    api_client.py      # HTTP API
```

## Quy tắc

- Backend Laravel → repo riêng, không gộp vào Python
- Branding tập trung `app_branding.py`
- `multiprocessing.freeze_support()` trước GUI
